    "name": "Effect: Shroud of Burning Pages",
    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>The odvolos is surrounded by an aura of burning paper and scorched parchment, which provides concealment as if it was smoke. A creature within the aura takes a –2 circumstance penalty to Perception checks, and a creature that ends its turn in the aura must succeed at a @Check[reflex|dc:22] save or any items with written information held or carried by the creature takes @Damage[1d4[persistent,fire]] damage. Magical items and religious texts are immune to this effect.</p>"
